dlxs::genSortForm()

Description
    public string dlxs::genSortForm(string $xml)
	Generates the appropriate markup for a drop down menu form.
	
Parameters
    xml
    	An xml string containing the $xml->SortOptionsMenu element.

Return Values
    A string containing the markup used to create a form for the purpose of sorting results.

Examples
	<?
	...
	print $dlxs->genSortForm($xml);
	...
	?>

Notes

See Also
	dlxs::genReference()